Title: Sole in mountains
DateModified: '2018-02-20'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/sole-in-mountains
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Virander singh  Chauhan
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "Their is hill station  called chakrata in uttrakhand. I lived their place is\
  \ blessed with nature. waterfall, leopard ,deer and many wild animal is very common\
  \ to get shown down. Their is palce called hanol which is around 70-75 km far from\
  \ chakrata  me and my frd had tracked that distance through mountain in two day\
  \ with lots of fun and adventure at some points in our journey from where  we can\
  \ see Himalayan mountains as we can see  Crystal clearly  this place is heaven on\
  \ earth untouched I had mesmerising experience over the trip which I can't explain\
  \ in words \nI alike to see nature closely so at regular interval I make plane to\
  \ this type of remote area to get in nature.. And feel real life.. Nature and beauty.\
  \ im nature lover \nMy sole lives in mountain I can't separate myself  from nature\
  \ and their beuty I had also travel main city and heritage sites also but my heart\
  \ lives in mountains."
